\subsection{Recommendations for Future Improvements}

\begin{enumerate}
	\item \textbf{Ground-truth validation}: Collect actual flood event polygons for robust model training;
	\item \textbf{Real-time weather integration}: Couple with IMD rainfall nowcasting for early warning;
	\item \textbf{HEC-RAS export}: Generate hydraulic model inputs for detailed flood simulation;
	\item \textbf{Mobile app interface}: Panchayati Raj officers need simple field access to drainage maps;
	\item \textbf{Multi-temporal analysis}: Process multi-year LiDAR to detect terrain changes;
	\item \textbf{Cloud deployment}: Dockerize pipeline for elastic processing on cloud infrastructure.
\end{enumerate}

The open-source codebase invites community contributions toward these extensions.

